                    Safe Gut & Mucking - cleaning out households. <a href="https://mutualaiddisasterrelief.org/safety-diy-cleanup/">Examples from Mutual Aid Disaster Relief</a>
                  </Todo>
                  <Todo id="skill-safe-food-prep" moduleKey="community-building" client:load>
                    <a href="https://www.vtchamber.com/servsafe/">Safe Food Prep</a>
                  </Todo>
                  <Todo id="skill-mapping" moduleKey="community-building" client:load>
